<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DevSecOps Project</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header {
            background: #35424a;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>DevSecOps Project</h1>
        <p>Deployed with AWS ECS, CodePipeline, and Terraform</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to our Application</h2>
            <p>This application was deployed using a complete CI/CD pipeline with security best practices.</p>
            <p>Infrastructure components:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>VPC with public and private subnets</li>
                <li>ECS Fargate for container orchestration</li>
                <li>RDS MySQL database</li>
                <li>CodePipeline for continuous delivery</li>
                <li>Security groups and IAM roles with least privilege</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
